Sosboot for Toshiba AC100
=========================

This is small embedded system for Toshiba AC100 recovery.

Get sources
===========

Install git-repo:

$ curl https://storage.googleapis.com/git-repo-downloads/repo > ~/bin/repo
$ chmod a+x ~/bin/repo


Init repo manifest in some folder:
repo init -u git://github.com/ac100-ru/sosboot-manifests.git -b sosboot-ng

Download system sources:
repo sync

Build Requirements
==================

Dont forget to install dtc, fakeroot and perl File::Slurp

Compile
=======

Run ./build_all bash script or scipts in ./scripts folder for individual parts

Clean
=====

Run ./clean_all bash script or clean_* scripts in ./scripts folder to clean
binaries for individual parts
